\begin_inset Formula $1/\sqrt{N}$
\end_inset

 where 
\begin_inset Formula $N=N_{E},N_{I}$
\end_inset

 respectively 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Output spiking-rate is given by the LIF neuron equation using 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu_{Q},\sigma_{Q}^{2}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\tau_{Q}$
\end_inset

 above 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
More general equation for the emission rate and a equation for the stationary
